title: Strife (Any%, Bad Ending, ZDoom) [21:13] (RTA)
description: So I picked this up over the weekend because I was bored and wanted to play something easier than shogo and wolfenstein. I am having a lot of fun with this game so far. I run on ZDoom because that version allows you to rocket jump and the one run I found on youtube does that. Once I beat that time I may start using veteran edition and go for the best ending.
